---
title: Baked Oregano Chicken with Rosemary Parmesan Fries
description: This oregano chicken, marinated in Greek yoghurt, is a simple combination that has been tried-and-tested and never fails to deliver a tender and flavoursome result. Served alongside the cheesy herb fries, this dish is sure to be a hit.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b7a41e230006c0cc801a284-ff8cc5b7.jpg
